    <title>Hexo搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/~lxp2298028871/2021/11/15/start-hexo/"/>
    <url>/~lxp2298028871/2021/11/15/start-hexo/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="安装Git"><a href="#安装Git" class="headerlink" title="安装Git"></a>安装Git</h4><ul><li><p>官网安装即可，只需修改安装目录即可，现在的最新版Git_2.33默认会将目录放入环境变量.</p></li><li><p>鼠标右键打开Git Bash ，设置<code>user.name</code>和<code>user.email</code></p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的GitHub用户名&quot;</span><br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>将Git绑定远程Github账号</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行上述指令，三个回车，然后复制<code>~/.ssh</code>文件夹下的<code>id_rsa.pub</code>文件内容</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh<br>$ vim id_rsa.pub<br><span class="hljs-comment">#vim复制快捷键为v,鼠标选中，按v即复制</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>进入Github个人账号，Setting=&gt;SSH and GPGkeys=&gt;New SSH key</p></li><li><p>验证是否成功</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ssh -T git@github.com<br><span class="hljs-comment">#如下输出正确</span><br>Hi ***! You<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安装Node-js"><a href="#安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="安装Node.js"></a>安装Node.js</h4><ul><li>官网下载安装即可，可能会下载很多东西，耐心等待即可，默认会将路径添加到PATH</li><li>检测是否安装成功<code>npm v</code></li></ul><h4 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h4><ul><li>使用<code>npm</code>安装Hexo</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="运行Hexo"><a href="#运行Hexo" class="headerlink" title="运行Hexo"></a>运行Hexo</h4><ul><li><p><code>npx hexo &lt;command&gt;</code></p></li><li><p>将Hexo所在目录下的<code>node_module</code>添加到环境变量，然后<code>hexo &lt;command&gt;</code>即可</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;PATH=&quot;$PATH:./node_modules/.bin&quot;&#x27;</span> &gt;&gt; ~/.profile<br><span class="hljs-comment">#执行上面这个命令时，cmd必须处于Node的安装目录下。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#比如Node.js安装在&#x27;D:\Hexo\Node&#x27;,那么在这里执行npm install -g hexo-cli就会在这个文件夹下面生成node_module文件夹，可以手动将node_module下的.bin文件夹加入环境变量</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="建站"><a href="#建站" class="headerlink" title="建站"></a>建站</h4><ul><li>修改<code>npm</code>下载镜像源，否则<code>npm install</code>很慢</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm config <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>在指定文件夹新建所需要的文件</p><p>==以下命令在空文件下执行才行==</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo init blog<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> blog<br>npm install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>修改主题</li></ul><p>使用<code>fluid</code>主题，<a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">hexo-theme-fluid</a></p><p>主题使用方法见上方链接。</p><p>按照<code>fluid</code>主题README.md文件完成后，测试一下网站雏形</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new test_my_site<br>hexo g<br>hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>上述命令执行后，在浏览器输入地址<code>localhost:40000</code>即可显示主页。</p><h4 id="Hexo常用命令"><a href="#Hexo常用命令" class="headerlink" title="Hexo常用命令"></a>Hexo常用命令</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo -g <span class="hljs-comment">#安装Hexo</span><br>npm update hexo -g <span class="hljs-comment">#升级</span><br>hexo init <span class="hljs-comment">#初始化博客</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 命令简写</span><br>hexo n my_blog == hexo new my_blog <span class="hljs-comment">#新建文章</span><br>hexo g == hexo generate <span class="hljs-comment">#生成</span><br>hexo s == hexo server <span class="hljs-comment">#启动服务预览</span><br>hexo d == hexo deploy <span class="hljs-comment">#部署</span><br><br>hexo server <span class="hljs-comment">#自动更新</span><br>hexo server -s <span class="hljs-comment">#静态模式</span><br>hexo server -p 5000 <span class="hljs-comment">#更改端口</span><br>hexo server -i 192.168.1.1 <span class="hljs-comment">#自定义 IP</span><br>hexo clean <span class="hljs-comment">#清除缓存，若是网页正常情况下可以忽略这条命令</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最常用的命令其实就三个</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo n blog_text<br>hexo g<br>hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>建立好的文章在<code>./source/_posts/</code>下，修改.md文件即可编辑文章</li></ul><h4 id="常见错误"><a href="#常见错误" class="headerlink" title="常见错误"></a>常见错误</h4><ul><li>新建的文章<code>--- ---</code>中的是标题、作者等信息，必须按照<code>npm</code>的规范书写</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">---<br>title: Hexo搭建个人博客<br><span class="hljs-comment">#title:[空格]标题    #空格必须有</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#title: “标题” #如果标题中有双引号要用中文双引号</span><br>date: 2021-11-15 22:16:30<br><span class="hljs-comment">#添加多个tags的规范，注意 -[空格]Hexo #同样要有空格</span><br>tags: <br>- Hexo<br>- HTML<br>---<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="将Hexo与Github关联"><a href="#将Hexo与Github关联" class="headerlink" title="将Hexo与Github关联"></a>将Hexo与Github关联</h4>]]></content>
    
    
    
